arStrings.szText: Taissa has sent Lorath and Neyrelle deep into the marshes to look for someone named Timue who holds the secret of how to find the Tree of Whispers.

Timue's cryptic instructions mention being tested by "The Swamp". Whatever that means, I need to find the ruins of a town called Yngovani and enter a temple of snake worship. There I will find a special incense needed for this test.
I have opened the temple built into the cave on the edge of Yngovani. The incense must be inside, but I suspect, so is a fierce snake named Mohlon.
